hopobject.body: Very interesting tale best drugstore foundation for daily wear It’s everybody’s fault but your own Katherine Jackson. The fact is that Michael was a drug addict for years. Who’s fault was that? Humm, lets see, Maybe your it was Joe’s fault! Nah, couldn’t be him because you can’t sue Joe. Maybe it was his siblings fault! Nah, they are as screwed up as Michael was. Maybe it was dare I say it? Your fault! Nah, your his innocent mother that has always stayed in the background and your husband beat the crap out of your children. Okay so we have pretty much ruled out your entire messed up family. Wait a minute, I think I have figured it out. How about Michael? Yes, that’s it. He was the idiot that overdosed himself. He asked for the drugs. He hired Conrad Murray to administer the drugs. He liked to have little boys sleep over and play fun games with Jesus Juice. I am sorry Kathrine that you and your perverted sick family doesn’t have your piggy bank anymore. But I am sure that the public is getting tried of all your crap. Oh one more thing, Tell Prince Michael that he can’t act and riding on the coat tails of his “Father” is just plain stupid.
